     C**JW1      L6KSSU    DIV  L6SYOS    WKHAK1  91
      *
JW1  C           L6SYOS    IFEQ 0
 .   C                     Z-ADD0         WKHAK1
 .   C                     ELSE
 .   C           L6KSSU    DIV  L6SYOS    WKHAK1  91
JW1  C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           WKHAK1    ADD  0.9       WKMAIS  50
